## Educational Use Notice

This project is designed for **academic and educational purposes**. While the
MIT License permits commercial use, please note:

- This environment uses simplified security configurations suitable for learning
- Default credentials are intentionally weak for educational accessibility
- No authentication on some services (e.g., Node-RED, Mosquitto)
- For production IIoT deployments, implement proper security measures:
  - Strong authentication and authorization
  - TLS/SSL encryption for all services
  - Network isolation and firewall rules
  - Secure credential management (secrets, vaults)
  - Regular security updates and patches
  - Compliance with industrial security standards (IEC 62443, etc.)

**DO NOT deploy this configuration directly to production environments.**

